OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill start cloudy with rain. It will
OL,7,Fthen turn clearer and drier from the
OL,8,Fwest for a time. Occasional showers
OL,9,Fthen setting in overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FFrequent blustery showers
OL,12,Fand gale force winds. A brighter
OL,13,Fafternoon with more sunny intervals
OL,14,Fbut still some showers. Winds slowly
OL,15,Feasing.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,18,Frain then blustery showers on
OL,19,FThursday, gales. Colder with sunshine
OL,20,Fand showers on Friday. Remaining
OL,21,Fshowery on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
